{% set preRepsDescText %}
<p class="govuk-body">
	At this stage you can <a href='/having-your-say-guide/registering-have-your-say' class="govuk-link">register to have your say</a> about the proposed project.
	This page will be updated when the registration period opens. You can view the project application documents to find out more about the application.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
	<a href='/having-your-say-guide/registering-have-your-say' class="govuk-link">
		Find out more about registering to have your say.
	</a>
</p>
{% endset %}

{% set repsOpenDescText %}
<p class="govuk-body">
		If you want to comment on this proposed project, you can now <a href='/having-your-say-guide/registering-have-your-say' class="govuk-link">register to have your say</a>.
		{% if applicationData.DateOfRelevantRepresentationClose %}Registration closes on {{ applicationData.DateOfRelevantRepresentationClose | date }} at 23:59.{% endif %}
</p>

<a href='/projects/{{ caseRef }}/register/register-have-your-say' class="govuk-button">
	Register to have your say
</a>
{% endset %}

{% set repsClosedDescText %}
<p class="govuk-body">
	The registration period to have your say about this project has closed.
	If you are not registered and you submit information during the examination stage, this may not be included.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
	Contact the project case team to find out more about how to get involved if you are not registered.
</p>

{% include '../_includes/email-request-text.njk' %}
{% endset %}

{% set repsPublishedDescText %}
<p class="govuk-body">
	We have now published all registration comments.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
	You can <a href='/projects/{{ caseRef }}/representations' class="govuk-link">view comments from other people who registered</a>.
</p>

{% include '../_includes/email-request-text.njk' %}
{% endset %}

{% set preLimDescText %}
{% if applicationData.DateOfPreliminaryMeeting %}
	<p class="govuk-body">
			The preliminary meeting for this project is on: {{ applicationData.DateOfPreliminaryMeeting  | date }}
	</p>
{% endif %}

<p class="govuk-body">
	You can check the <a href='{{ rule6Document.path }}' target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"  class="govuk-link">rule 6 letter</a> to find out how to get involved.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
	In this meeting, the Examining Authority sets out how they examine the application. This includes the examination timetable and the issues they will focus on during examination.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
	<a href='/having-your-say-guide/get-involved-preliminary-meeting' class="govuk-link">Find out more about getting involved in the preliminary meeting</a>
</p>

{% include '../_includes/email-request-text.njk' %}
{% endset %}

